  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its bulk, massing, scale, detailed design, position and location, would result in an incongruous and incompatible form of development would have a detrimental impact upon the character and appearance of the host building and would fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of this part of the Clapton Square Conservation Area. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D1, D3, D4 and HC1, policies LP1, LP3 of the Local Plan 2033 and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009 and the NPPF (2023).&lt;/p&gt;"
